00:00:33.266 --> 00:00:34.620
<v Jay McKay> Hello, everyone.

00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:37.750
Welcome to WordPress
Accessibility Day.

00:00:37.750 --> 00:00:41.500
My name is Jay McKay, and I am
the Director of Community Programs

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.180
at Nobility.

