that have been prerecorded.

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:54.590
Our first talk will be Can the
Cloud Accelerate Accessibility,

00:00:54.590 --> 00:00:59.310
presented by, Robert Jacobi, who’s
Director of WordPress, Cloudways.

00:00:59.310 --> 00:01:04.530
The second talk will be Aria
